Doctors.name: Swapna Gandhe
Doctors.about:
She has performed 3000 SICS including topical SICS and 50 ECCE.
She also specializes in refractive surgeries like LASIK, PRK, Phakic IOL (ICL/IPCL), Multifocal IOL, toric IOL, Trifocal IOL

Worked as Senior Retina Consultant at Contacare Eye Hospitals ( 2016 to 2018)
Experience in more than 3000 Retina surgeries and more than 10,000 Retina procedures (lasers, intravitreal injections)
Presented many papers and given talks at BOA, Maharashtra Ophthalmic Association annual conferences
